As a User

# Authentication

I want to register/login with Facebook
So that I can access the app with minimum fuss

# Queueing
I want to see Queue times for nearby Places
So that I can decide whether it's worth my while going

I want to see Queue times for a particular Place
So that I can see Places that are of interest not just nearby

I want to see more detailed Queueing stats for a particular Place
So that I can make a more informed decision about whether to going there

I want to record my time in the Queue
So that I can get points and


# Leaderboard
As an Exec
I want to show a Leaderboard of the best performing Queuers
So that I can encourage Users to records their Queues more